ygData.subject: Re: hunting spots
ygData.msgSnippet: Have you tried Najena then.. I sometimes go there (Lvl 15), but can t go to far in due to a tentacle (sp?) terror that likes hanging out near the entrance,
ygData.messageBody:
Have you tried Najena then.. I sometimes go there (Lvl 15), but can't go to
far in due to a tentacle (sp?) terror that likes hanging out near the
entrance, also I haven't tried it yet but I hear Cazic-Thule has some good
hunting.
